---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Insights"
description: "Thoughts on technology and the world we live in."
ogSlug: insights
---
<section class="section wrap">
  <div class="eyebrow">Insights</div>
  <h1>Thoughts on technology and the world we live in.</h1>
  <p class="lead" style="max-width: 640px;">
    Short, direct takes, not summaries of someone else's newsletter. Cross-posted to
    <a href="{{ site.linkedin }}" style="color: var(--rg-red);">LinkedIn</a> every week.
  </p>

  <h2 class="visually-hidden">All Posts</h2>
  <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
    {% for post in collections.posts %}
    <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-list__item">
      <div>
        <h3 class="post-list__title">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
        <p class="small" style="margin: 0.4rem 0 0; color: var(--rg-slate);">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      </div>
      <span class="post-list__meta">{{ post.data.date | readableDate }}</span>
    </a>
    {% else %}
    <p>First post is coming soon.</p>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
